headline: Armis Rapidly Surpasses $300M ARR as Demand For Cyber Exposure Management and Cyber-Physical Systems Security Soars
summary: LAS VEGAS, August 04, 2025--Black Hat—Armis, the cyber exposure management & security company, today announced another major milestone as it rapidly surpassed $300 million in annual recurring revenue (ARR), growing from $200m in ARR in less than 12 months.
